<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Axiom_of_choice&amp;action=edit&amp;section=15" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">References</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Herrlich, Horst, <i>Axiom of Choice</i>, Springer Lecture Notes in Mathematics 1876, Springer Verlag Berlin Heidelberg (2006). <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/3540309896" class="internal">ISBN 3-540-30989-6</a>.</li>
<li>Paul Howard and Jean Rubin, "Consequences of the Axiom of Choice". Mathematical Surveys and Monographs 59; American Mathematical Society; 1998.</li>
<li>Thomas Jech, "About the Axiom of Choice." <i>Handbook of Mathematical Logic</i>, John Barwise, ed., 1977.</li>
<li>Gregory H Moore, "Zermelo's axiom of choice, Its origins, development and influence", Springer; 1982. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0387906703" class="internal">ISBN 0-387-90670-3</a></li>
<li>Ernst Zermelo, "Untersuchungen über die Grundlagen der Mengenlehre I," <i>Mathematische Annalen 65</i>: (1908) pp. 261-81. <a href="http://www.digizeitschriften.de/no_cache/home/jkdigitools/loader/?tx_jkDigiTools_pi1%5BIDDOC%5D=361762" class="external text" title="http://www.digizeitschriften.de/no_cache/home/jkdigitools/loader/?tx_jkDigiTools_pi1%5BIDDOC%5D=361762" rel="nofollow">PDF download via digizeitschriften.de</a></li>
</ul>
